casebody.data:
Butler v. Jarvis. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 24, 1889.) For hearing on appeal, see 4 H. Y. Supp. 138.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Daniels and Bartlett, JJ.

Ho opinion. Stay on the judgment on appeal to the court of appeals ordered and allowed: but not to prevent the collection of securities deposited for the benefit of the plaintiff.
